OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA damp and cloudy start on
OL,6,FMonday will soon give way to sunny
OL,7,Fspells from mid-morning. Continuing to
OL,8,Ffeel rather cold with mostly light
OL,9,Fwinds, however it will become breezy
OL,10,Fnear coasts later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry overnight with variable
OL,13,Famounts of cloud and lengthy clear
OL,14,Fspells developing. An early dip in
OL,15,Ftemperatures before cloudier skies and
OL,16,Fpatchy rain arrives across the region
OL,17,Ftowards dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
