OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloudy with patchy rain
OL,6,Facross the region from early morning.
OL,7,FSoon turning brighter with sunny
OL,8,Fspells developing from the north.
OL,9,FBecoming increasingly blustery into
OL,10,Fthe afternoon with scattered showers
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,12,
OL,13,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,14,FBlustery with sunny spells and heavy
OL,15,Fshowers on both Wednesday and
OL,16,FThursday. More settled on Friday with
OL,17,Fdrier and brighter conditions.
OL,18,FRemaining chilly, with a risk of frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
